sentences: Anthony Leonard Platt (born November 28, 1981)  commonly known by his stage name Unk, is an American DJ, hype man, and rapper.
He is best known for the mid 2000s snap hit "Walk It Out".
He began spinning records in 1998, and, after meeting DJ Jelly and DJ Montay, joined their DJ entourage, the Southern Style DJs.
In 2000, Big Oomp signed Unk to his label, Big Oomp Records.
in 2006 led by the single "Walk It Out" that reached Billboard Hot 100 top 10.
In 2009 he suffered health-issues that resulted in a reduced profile.
In 2013 he released the single "Have A Toast" followed by "Wait" in 2014, while he continues to tour the college circuit.
